  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Logistic supervisor",
  "description": "<p><strong>About the Role:</strong><br />We are looking for a reliable and safety-focused<strong> Logistics Supervisor</strong> to join our team. In this role, you will be responsible for delivering goods with the driver to customers in a timely and professional manner while ensuring all company and road safety regulations are followed.</p><p><strong>Key Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Supervise and coordinate with drivers in the team</li><li>Load, transport, and deliver products to various locations</li><li>Follow assigned routes and schedules</li><li>Maintain delivery records and paperwork</li><li>Provide friendly and professional customer service</li><li>Inspect vehicle before and after trips and report any issues</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Ability to lift and move packages as needed</li><li>Good communication and time-management skills</li><li>Reliability and a strong work ethic</li></ul>",
